Package model

Class customersModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.customersModel
  • public class customersModel
extends java.lang.Object
    Customers class represents customer information and provides methods to access and manipulate customer data. It contains attributes such as customerID, customerName, customerAddress, customerPostalCode, customerPhoneNumber, divisionID, and divisionName. The class includes setters and getters for each attribute to facilitate functionality and data management.
